OL,3,CFamily's tribute after missing man's
OL,4,Cbody found in woods six years on
OL,6,FThe family of a man whose body was
OL,7,Ffound in woodland next to a bypass in
OL,8,FMansfield say it is "strange and
OL,9,Fimpossible" to put their feelings into
OL,10,Fwords.
OL,12,FMichael Dennington was 58 when he was
OL,13,Freported missing by his family in May
OL,14,F2020 having last been seen at Kings
OL,15,FMill Hospital in Sutton-in-Ashfield.
OL,17,FMembers of the public found his
OL,18,Fremains six years later, on 23 May
OL,19,Fthis year, in woodland next to the
OL,20,FA617 Rainworth Bypass.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
