PN,33502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1783682372
OL,3,CFamily's tribute after missing man's
OL,4,Cbody found in woods six years on
OL,6,FIn a tribute to Mr Dennington, his son
OL,7,Fsaid: "For many years, I've looked up
OL,8,Fto you. You had a good heart and
OL,9,Falways cared for those around you.
OL,11,F"I remember growing up as a kid,
OL,12,Fwalking to the shops with you. You'd
OL,13,Fmake me laugh and give me a hand full
OL,14,Fof change to buy sweets.
OL,16,F"There were many things I wanted to
OL,17,Fshow you throughout my journey in
OL,18,Flife, and many things I won't be able
OL,19,Fto now.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1783682372
OL,3,CFamily's tribute after missing man's
OL,4,Cbody found in woods six years on
OL,6,FHis daughter added: "Dad, it's strange
OL,7,Fand impossible to put into words what
OL,8,Fwe are feeling.
OL,10,F"For years you were our dad. Dad, you
OL,11,Fshaped part of who we are today. Rest
OL,12,Fin peace, love you."
OL,14,FSpecialist archaeologists and
OL,15,Fanthropologists have been working at
OL,16,Fthe site and Nottinghamshire Police
OL,17,Fsay a team of detectives continue to
OL,18,Finvestigate the circumstances
OL,19,Fsurrounding Mr Dennington's death and
OL,20,Fare still waiting for the final post-
OL,21,Fmortem findings.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
